, i.e., a HS-LS frustration, up to high pressure. Our results\ndemonstrate the importance of quantum fluctuations of the valence and spin\nstates for the understanding of quantum criticality of the Mott transitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 17:28:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-22"}
