escence of voids leading to failure\nappears related to local instabilities in the form of shear band formation and\nis therefore only indirectly determined by the global stress state in that it\ndetermines the global distribution, density and size of voids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 11:05:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-05"}
